I"=<p>Need for authenticity - one of our core needs is the ability to feel like we can bring our full self to our relationships. 
Need for connection - we all have a need to feel like we are seen, understood and valued in our relationships.
This module explores how by developing our authenticity we can enjoy more fulfilling and connected relationships with others. 
You will learn how these two needs are interrelated and how by understanding how to recognise and express your needs in relationships you can experience more fulfilling and close connections with others.</p>
